title: Cangshu Leyuan
synopsis: To the east of the Happy Forest, there is a mysterious hamster paradise where many cute hamsters live. The protagonist of the story is the sporty and brave "Hapi Dan", the gluttonous and chubby "Lard Dan", and the beauty The kind-hearted "Little Tangdan", the young but fearless "Little Fudan", the director of "Einstein" who often invents and so on. But on the other side of the Happy Forest, there is an Eagle-Wei brand company composed of natural enemies of hamsters, with the boss "Yi Gao" (eagle), "Fox Jingli" (fox), "Shlick" (snake), Yi Gao's secretary "Wuyaya" (crow). (translated from iqiyi)

title: Jin Tong Wang Shijie

A girl named Pu Jinxi broke into his life, which made Tong Hua extremely unaccustomed. He tried every means to fight Jinxi, trying to force him to leave. But every time, Jinxi can always deal with it freely, let Tong Hua be boring. Over time, they slowly changed from opposition to understanding, and began to tolerate each other, and the beautiful youth story opened a new page. (translated from iqiyi)

Their job is to help children achieve their true, kind, and beautiful birthday wishes, so that their wishes come true and their dreams come true. Tiantian, Qianqian, Tuantuan, and Mumu are four lively and lovely birthday elves. They assist the birthday grandpa to help the children fulfill their birthday wishes. Whenever the birthday grandfather stamped a dream come true, they will come to the children to help them fulfill their wishes, leap wonderfully, and have an extraordinary birthday journey. Every time helping children fulfill their wishes is a happy challenge for them.(translated from iqiyi)

title: Tao

Suddenly one day, while playing wildly in the woods with her good friend Panda Dongdong, the fairy school fairy Dudu came to grandpa with a letter of admission from Tao... (translated form iqiyi)

title: Gaotie Xia

In order to reproduce the prosperity of Monster Mountain, the heir to the property right of Monster Mountain opened a simulation amusement park company, recruiting many different characters. Different companions, experienced all kinds of difficulties and interesting things, and finally managed to become a happy paradise. (ranslated from iqiyi)

title: Chaohu Chuanshuo
synopsis: Legend has it that in ancient times, there was a Huang Batian dominating one side in Chaozhou City. There was a severe drought in Chaozhou this year, and the people didn't have a chance to live. One day, Jiao Yugu and grandma Jiao, who lived in the city, were walking outside, and they came across a little white dragon who was practicing as a white turtle and took it home. Huang Batian wants to forcefully marry Yugu, and Bailong helps him. Grandma Jiao begged Bailong to rain to save the people of Chaozhou. Bailong privately dropped heavy rain, violated the rules of heaven, and was fined to the world. Huang Batian designed to frame the white dragon and gain immortality and invincible power. Bailong gave the dragon ball to Yugu and brought it back to the East China Sea. After being infiltrated by sea water, the white dragon was reborn in the dragon ball. In order to avoid the invincible Huang Batian, the Jade Emperor ordered Chaozhou to sink to the bottom. Bailong struggled to deal with the heavenly soldiers, while Yugu and grandma led the people of Yizhou out of Chaozhou City. Finally, the flood flooded the sinking Chaozhou City and Huang Batian into the bottom of the water, turning it into the current Chaohu Lake. Bailong, Yugu and Grandma joined together, and took the people to the distance by boat, and started a new life.(translated from iqiyi)

Along the way, Fang Qiniang went through various magical situations and encountered various difficulties. In the process, she gradually discovered her potential and learned one of the legendary methods of Baihe Quan, "Cunjin Relay". Finally, Fang Qiniang gathered five feathers, soaked them with bergamot tea, and melted them into a roll of colorful slender ribbons. Fang Qiniang intertwined the ribbon with the portrait of her mother that she carried with him. The portrait of her mother began to become blurred and three-dimensional. Fang Qiniang saw her mother in an instant...(translated from iqiyi)

It is based on the main line of this story. , And added some philosophical and educational storylines to achieve the effect of entertaining and entertaining. On the other hand, the story focuses on the transformation of the young Hua Tuo’s mentality-how to elevate from a child who simply wants to be a doctor to understand the principle of suspending the pot to help the world, and then grow up step by step, and finally comprehend how to treat the country, Chinese medicine, and people. The spiritual connotation of medical treatment. (translated form iqiyi)

With the help of Hachiko and his friends, he traveled through the "Twenty-Four Solar Terms" time and time again to find the bamboo slips scattered a hundred years ago. During the adventure, Honglie and his partner Ji Ming Gou Diao experienced the spirit of ancient myths, appreciated the wisdom of the predecessors in the Spring and Autumn Period, and saw the strange things among ordinary people. At this time, the scientists found the baby dinosaurs, and they were surprised to find that the spiritual civilization index of the 4 baby dinosaurs were all full marks. Through a series of stories that happened in the guinea pig town, everyone learned about traffic safety, fire safety, and off-campus safety, so that everyone can effectively avoid disasters and learn how to save themselves. (translated from youku)

title: Tunshu Xiao Zhen Zhi Le You Da Shijie
synopsis: The mayor of Guinea Pig Town invented the "Guoxue Great Pass" experience house. He brought the residents of Guinea Pig Town into the world of Sinology, allowing them to learn about Sinology. However, the invention house was destroyed by Mr. Virus. If he cannot pass the checkpoint set by Mr. Virus, he cannot get out of the invention house. As a result, everyone constantly solved various problems, defeated Mr. Virus again and again, and learned a lot of knowledge. (translated from tendceng)

details.Japanese: 豚鼠小镇之乐游大世界

title: Tunshu Zhi Shi Wan Ge Weisheme
synopsis: Juezhu and Baby Guinea Pig are two brothers, and the knowledgeable Ji Mu is their favorite neighbor's eldest brother. Whenever the two little guys encountered various problems, they would consult Yoshimu, and Yoshimu was always able to help them in time. Ji Mu also took the two little guys to the bottom of the sea, to the forest, and even to space, to learn about everything they were interested in. (translated from tenceng)

title: Tunshu Zhen Kuaile Shenghuo Zhi Yanyu Leyuan
synopsis: A group of happy and lively little guinea pigs live in Guinea Pig Town: enthusiastic and knowledgeable Ji Mu, kind-hearted and beautiful cool girl, studious and timid little guinea pig, Ziluo who loves inventing, and a delicious and lazy sleeper. There is also a pair of guys in the town who are often troublesome and disruptive-the Thunder Dragon and Thunder Tiger brothers. They often cause trouble to the little guinea pigs and destroy the feelings between them. But fortunately, there are the mayor’s grandfather and the sensible Ji Mu. Every time they can solve the troubles caused by the ridiculous brothers and resolve everyone's conflicts.(translated from tenceng)

details.Japanese: 豚鼠镇快乐生活之谚语乐园

title: Bu Erduo De Gushi
synopsis: The cartoonist gave the protagonist in the comic a nice name, Bu Er. Bao Hulu struggled hard for his ideals and bread in his semi-underground studio. One day, when he woke up, he found that he had moved into the comics he had created. Although Bao Hulu wanted to return to reality, things were not so easy. In his cartoon world, a series of strange things happened to Bao Hulu and his characters Bu Er, Cake Tou and others... (translated from iqiyi)

title: Haixing Xiongdi
synopsis: Venus, Jupiter, Mercury, Mars and Saturn are five small starfishes with special skills. They live in the beautiful and fertile Coral Sea with Grandpa Taiguxing. Noisy squid and two of his men are alien pirates, and they stared at the corals in the Coral Sea. The starfish have stopped the alien pirates' plots to steal coral again and again (translated from iqiyi)

title: Senlin Hao Huoban Zhi Kuaile Shenghuo

title: Jigokuraku
synopsis: Gabimaru the Hollow, a ninja of Iwagakure Village known for being cold and emotionless, was set up by his fellow ninja and is now on death row. Tired of killing and betrayal, he wants to die. However, no method of execution works on him because as much as the seemingly apathetic Gabimaru refuses to admit it, he does have a reason to live. He wants to return to his wife, who was the reason why he softened up and failed to be an effective assassin. Thus, he refuses to die. Asaemon the Decapitator, a famous executioner, sees this and has a proposal for the ninja. He wants Gabimaru to join an expedition to an island south of Japan in search of the elixir of life in exchange for a full pardon by the Shogunate. However, this island isn't a normal island: it's believed to be Paradise. However the island is full of mysteries, and the exploring team—consisting of those marked for death—might not be fully prepared to handle them.

title: Kuaile Baobei Zhi Xingqu Mofang

In the Bee Garden series, the donut babies are transformed into cute little bees, honest caterpillars and hardworking fireflies. title: Baosheng Dadi Zhi Qi Er Duo Bao
synopsis: "The Wonderful Treasure of Baosheng Emperor" tells the story of Wu Kui's determination to study medicine since he was a child. After many trials, he successfully worshipped Bai Bodhi as his teacher and embarked on the journey of medicine. On the remote Kunlun Mountains, the medical sage Wujizi devoted himself to practicing, just to decipher the "wordless heavenly book", to master the peak medical skills, and to benefit the people of Li people. However, even if the opportunity is not here, even if he does his best, he can only regret to retreat. Before the retreat, he explained to his apprentice Bai Bo that he was looking for a soul boy with the five spirits, four difficulties, and three treasures in his hands. After finding, together with Xuanfeng who went down the mountain privately, he accepted the soul boy as an apprentice, and selflessly inherited the essence of traditional Chinese medicine of yin and yang. He also assisted the soul boy to gather the five spirits, overcome the four difficulties, and win the three treasures. With a mysterious task, Bai Bodhi traveled all the way to the village where Wu Kui lived, and began to look for a magical soul boy. This soul boy later became a generation of God of Medicine-Baosheng Emperor.(translated from iqiyi)
